Function Detail

tk_dbisearch_browse

void tk_dbisearch_browse ( &$this, [$g_begin = ''], [$g_prev = ''], [$g_next = ''], [$g_end = ''] )

Print widget to browse dbisearch results. 
This widget occupies a row. tk_dbisearch() must be used before.
 If there's no more than one page nothing is printed at all.
Function Parameters:
- object $this: application
- string $g_begin: Path to image for link to first record.
- string $g_prev: Path to image for link to previous record.
- string $g_next: Path to image for link to next record.
- string $g_end: Path to image for link to last record.
Function Info:
See - tk_dbisearch()
Access - public
